pageContext.claim: “I've actually never heard "four more years." That's an interesting one. We'll go for six, and then we'll all be in very good shape.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has undoubtedly heard "four more years." It is commonly chanted at political rallies for president's during their first term. He can't "go for six." There are two more years left in his first term. If he is reelected, that would equal four more years.
